reviewText: The woman's voice was easy to hear and understand.  The man's was pleasant but hardly audible.

A lot of chatting, three chords and that's it. I couldn't believe it when I realized I'd come to the end of the DVD!

You can learn more on YouTube in a few minutes.

No redeeming value. Can't imagine what they were thinking...

I'm sorry, this is the worst video ever.  The most helpful thing about this video is the insert with the ukulele chords.  The video is completely outdated, too much talking not enough teaching.  Don't buy it.
